article_title: Video: Stephen Colbert visits Monmouth's food bank to sign up for Obamacare
article_text:
In the latest edition of Steven Colbert’s “I Tried to Sign Up For Obamacare” segment, Colbert visits the The Food Bank of Monmouth and Ocean Counties.

In the video, Colbert sits down with Director Frank Rodriguez in the food bank’s kitchen to answer questions on how he can sign up for Obamacare, health care eligibility, contraception coverage and prostate exams.
